{
  "stem": "1502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then when we left, when we left his house, he gave us a basket with 200 hard-boiled eggs, so we should have food when-- our plans were to reach--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I do remember my-- my father had an uncle in Poland who was an extremely, generous, nice, good person.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to call him the [NON-ENGLISH] or uncle [NON-ENGLISH]-- Uncle Reuben.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we named this-- this man, this Belgian, we called him the [NON-ENGLISH], because he was so nice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, he gave us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our plans were to reach the sea-- the sea coast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because in World War I, when the Germans attacked Belgium, there was a tiny part of Belgium along the sea coast, which they never occupied.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we figured with the French and with the British army that came in to help, they will be able to hold the part of seacoast.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's where we wanted to reach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we couldn't, because we were-- we were cut off by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They reached the ocean before us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all the refugees, and all the armies that were in between were cut off-- so were the French, the-- the Belgians, the British, and the refugees.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were all cut off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We couldn't-- we couldn't get through anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All we could reach-- we reached a-- the big town in northern France-- Lille.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We reached Lille.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember we reached it before-- before the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We came to--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
